title: Innovation capacity analysis and services for SMEs in Thuringia
objective: The project applicant will provide innovation capacity analysis and advisory services for Thuringian SMEs with potential for internationalization. Furthermore, beneficiaries of the Horizon 2020 SME instrument will be supported by the project's key account managers in taking advantage of professional business coaching.
participants: STIFTUNG FUR TECHNOLOGIE INNOVATIONUND FORSCHUNG THURINGEN
